text:
btw, just fyr for PH promotions:

_Here’s how it works:_
• _Each day we promote 1 product that previously launched on PH._ 
• _The post is fixed in the 4th slot in the feed so that it’s prominently featured in the homepage_
• _If a user is not interested in the product, a small “X” close button will appear in the top right of the post so they can dismiss it from their feed._
• _Unlike non-promoted posts on the homepage, clicking the post opens a new tab your website directly. This is intended to focus on driving traffic to your site._
• _All Promoted Product partners will also be featured in the newsletter with your product logo and 200 character description, reaching more than 350,000 makers._
_*We promote one product a day for 24 hours (starting midnight PT) and is $4,000/day (normally $6,000), 2 days for $7000 and 3 days for $10,000.*_

elements.text: btw, just fyr for PH promotions:
Here’s how it works:
Each day we promote 1 product that previously launched on PH.
The post is fixed in the 4th slot in the feed so that it’s prominently featured in the homepage
If a user is not interested in the product, a small “X” close button will appear in the top right of the post so they can dismiss it from their feed.
Unlike non-promoted posts on the homepage, clicking the post opens a new tab your website directly. This is intended to focus on driving traffic to your site.
All Promoted Product partners will also be featured in the newsletter with your product logo and 200 character description, reaching more than 350,000 makers.
We promote one product a day for 24 hours (starting midnight PT) and is $4,000/day (normally $6,000), 2 days for $7000 and 3 days for $10,000.
